trans-unit.source: To implement a custom upgrade initiator, inherit from this <xref uid="langword_csharp_abstract" name="abstract" href=""></xref> base class.
trans-unit.target: Om du vill implementera en anpassad uppgradering initierare ärver från den här <xref uid="langword_csharp_abstract" name="abstract" href=""> </xref> basklassen.

trans-unit.source: An example of a stream upgrade is to build a compression stream directly on top of the transport stream.
trans-unit.target: Ett exempel på en uppgradering av dataströmmen är att skapa en komprimerad dataström direkt ovanpå transportdataströmmen.

trans-unit.source: This class is used with <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.StreamUpgradeAcceptor> and <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.StreamUpgradeProvider> to implement a custom stream upgrade.
trans-unit.target: Den här klassen används med <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.StreamUpgradeAcceptor>och <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.StreamUpgradeProvider>att genomföra en uppgradering av anpassade dataström.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.StreamUpgradeProvider> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.StreamUpgradeAcceptor>

trans-unit.source: For a detailed description of the upgrade process, see <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.StreamUpgradeProvider>.
trans-unit.target: En detaljerad beskrivning av uppgraderingen finns <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.StreamUpgradeProvider>.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.StreamUpgradeProvider>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Channels.StreamUpgradeInitiator"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Channels.StreamUpgradeInitiator"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: This <xref uid="langword_csharp_abstract" name="abstract" href=""></xref> method can be implemented to do asynchronous processing that initiates an upgrade.
trans-unit.target: Detta <xref uid="langword_csharp_abstract" name="abstract" href=""> </xref> metod kan implementeras för att göra asynkron bearbetning som initierar en uppgradering.

trans-unit.source: This method calls <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.StreamUpgradeInitiator.InitiateUpgrade%2A> and returns.
trans-unit.target: Den här metoden anropar <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.StreamUpgradeInitiator.InitiateUpgrade%2A>och returnerar.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.StreamUpgradeInitiator.InitiateUpgrade%2A>

trans-unit.source: The stream to be upgraded.
trans-unit.target: Dataströmmen som ska uppgraderas.

trans-unit.source: The method to call when the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.StreamUpgradeInitiator.InitiateUpgrade*> has completed.
trans-unit.target: Metoden du vill anropa när den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.StreamUpgradeInitiator.InitiateUpgrade*>har slutförts.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.StreamUpgradeInitiator.InitiateUpgrade*>

trans-unit.source: State information about the status of the asynchronous call.
trans-unit.target: Tillstånd information om status för asynkront anrop.

trans-unit.source: Returns an <xref:System.IAsyncResult> to be passed into the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.StreamUpgradeInitiator.EndInitiateUpgrade*> method.
trans-unit.target: Returnerar en <xref:System.IAsyncResult>som ska överföras till den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.StreamUpgradeInitiator.EndInitiateUpgrade*>metoden.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.StreamUpgradeInitiator.EndInitiateUpgrade*> </xref:System.IAsyncResult>

trans-unit.source: This method is the asynchronous callback method that is called after <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.StreamUpgradeInitiator.BeginInitiateUpgrade*> has completed.
trans-unit.target: Den här metoden är asynkront motanrop-metod som anropas när <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.StreamUpgradeInitiator.BeginInitiateUpgrade*>har slutförts.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.StreamUpgradeInitiator.BeginInitiateUpgrade*>

trans-unit.source: For more information about using this method, see the remarks in <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.StreamUpgradeInitiator.InitiateUpgrade%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Mer information om hur du använder den här metoden finns i anmärkningar i <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.StreamUpgradeInitiator.InitiateUpgrade%2A>.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.StreamUpgradeInitiator.InitiateUpgrade%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref uid="langword_csharp_IAsyncResult" name="IAsyncResult" href=""></xref> returned from the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.StreamUpgradeInitiator.BeginInitiateUpgrade*> method.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref uid="langword_csharp_IAsyncResult" name="IAsyncResult" href=""> </xref> returnerades från den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.StreamUpgradeInitiator.BeginInitiateUpgrade*>metoden.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.StreamUpgradeInitiator.BeginInitiateUpgrade*>

trans-unit.source: Returns the upgraded stream.
trans-unit.target: Returnerar den uppgraderade dataströmmen.

trans-unit.source: Returns the content type of the next upgrade to be performed.
trans-unit.target: Returnerar nästa uppgraderingen utförs innehållstyp.

trans-unit.source: This method returns a set of upgrade content types supported by the upgrade provider in the order in which they are expected.
trans-unit.target: Den här metoden returnerar en uppsättning uppgradera innehållstyper som stöds av uppgradera providern i den ordning som de förväntas.

trans-unit.source: Upgrade providers that support a single upgrade return only a single value.
trans-unit.target: Uppgradera providers som stöder en enkel uppgradering returnerar endast ett värde.

trans-unit.source: Upgrade providers that support multiple upgrades return the values in order (for example, compression content type followed by the security content type).
trans-unit.target: Uppgradera leverantörer som stöder flera uppgraderingar returnera värdena i ordning (till exempel komprimering innehållstyp följt av security content-type).

trans-unit.source: Returns the content type of the next upgrade.
trans-unit.target: Returnerar nästa uppgraderingen innehållstyp.

trans-unit.source: Initiates the upgrade of the stream by requesting the other end of its connection to upgrade the channel transport layer.
trans-unit.target: Initierar uppgraderingen av dataströmmen genom att begära den andra änden av anslutningen till uppgradera kanal Transportskiktet.

trans-unit.source: This method can be called multiple times for each upgrade supported by the upgrade provider.
trans-unit.target: Den här metoden kan anropas flera gånger för varje uppgradering uppgradera providern.

trans-unit.source: For example, an upgrade provider that supports compression and security would call this method twice: first to upgrade the default transport streaming for compression, and second to upgrade the security.
trans-unit.target: Till exempel en uppgradering provider som stöder komprimering och säkerhet skulle anropa den här metoden två gånger: först för att uppgradera Standardtransporten strömning för komprimering och andra för att uppgradera säkerheten.

trans-unit.source: Subsequent calls to this method should pass in the upgrade stream from the previous call.
trans-unit.target: Efterföljande anrop till den här metoden Överför i uppgraderingen dataströmmen från det föregående anropet.

trans-unit.source: The stream to be upgraded.
trans-unit.target: Dataströmmen som ska uppgraderas.

trans-unit.source: Returns the upgraded stream.
trans-unit.target: Returnerar den uppgraderade dataströmmen.
